    println("    chemistry_vqe  29,603 LoC  VQE chemistry suite (per-molecule CMT hamiltonians,")
    println("                              4e4o/4e5o/4e6o active spaces, kuPCCGSD + L-BFGS-B)")
    println("    surface_code_d3 · bench (per-molecule 4e4o benchmarks)")
    println("")
    println("  ABSORPTION: RFC 045 LANDED 2026-05-16 — 114 .hexa, all parse-clean.")
    println("  Modules invoked via `hexa qmirror <subcmd>` (subprocess dispatch).")
    println("  Archive: github.com/dancinlab/qmirror (private, frozen 묘비)")
